Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Networks refuse Ford air time
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z91zw
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Oct 1975
Ford's proposed TV speech on tax cuts judged 'illegal' by networks who refuse the president air time. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less